## Resources

**Tools:** Claude Code (primary)

**APIs:**
- Trading terminal API (data source)
- LOIS API (mock for demo, real for production)

**Help:**
- Terminal team: API questions
- LOIS team: Integration patterns

---

## Failsafe Plan

**Trigger:** End of Day 2 significantly behind

**Fallback:** Analysis rules + notification only (no LOIS trigger, no P&L tracking)

**Cut:**
- Paper trading performance tracking
- LOIS integration
- Multiple analysis types (just do one well)

**Keep:**
- Configurable analysis rules
- Real data, real analysis
- Demo that one rule works

