- Backtesting against historical data
- AI-suggested rules based on user trading history

---

## Tech Notes

**Architecture:**
```
User Config -> Analysis Engine (code, not AI) -> Trigger System -> Mock LOIS
                     |
                     v
            Paper Trading Tracker -> P&L Dashboard
```

**Key Decisions:**
- Claude helps BUILD analysis logic, doesn't RUN analysis at query time
- Deterministic code execution = fast, reliable, no hallucination risk
- Mock LOIS for demo = safe, clear path to production

